pd_0_com_0text: Hey, I'm new in town. My name's [PName]. what is there to do for fun around here?
pd_0_com_1text: You'll have to excuse me. I have trouble ignoring such alluring people.
pd_0_com_2text: Hey, I'm... I mean, uhh, you'll... never mind.
pd_1_com_0text: Oh, hello. I am Strannik. I eat and wander.
pd_2_com_0text: I have noticed the nearby dungeons just off of the town.
pd_3_com_0text: Then why are you here? Oh, you mean... me? Well, I am Strannik.
pd_4_com_0text: If the rumours are true, the monsters that dwell within them have even been posing a threat to the village.
pd_5_com_0text: If I see to it to venture into the dungeons would you be able to help me? It's dangerous to go alone after all.
pd_6_com_0text: I hit things with my halberd. I go where there are sights to see. It takes a lot to hurt me.
pd_7_com_0text: You sound like a valuable ally. I could use your help exploring the dungeons if you'd assist me?
pd_8_com_0text: I care little for money, but food is important. I will follow you if you promise such things.
pd_9_com_0text: How about this? Whatever you find in the dungeon, you get to keep.
pd_9_com_1text: Sorry, that's a little steep for me.
pd_13_com_2text: Tell me about your likes / dislikes
pd_14_com_0text: Could you tell me something about yourself?
pd_var_15_0: I found this harp during my travels. I am no good at playing it, but it's nice to listen to.
pd_var_15_1: I have wandered the lands for so long, it has become natural to me. There is a whole world to see, so I might as well go see it.
pd_var_15_2: I sharpen my halberd when there is nothing else to do. You never know when a fight may happen.
pd_16_com_0text: How do you feel about us?
